---

---

<section id="ia" class="ai-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ai-content">
      <div class="ai-badge">
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            d="M12 2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2c0 .74-.4 1.39-1 1.73V7h1a7 7 0 0 1 7 7h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1a7 7 0 0 1 7-7h1V5.73c-.6-.34-1-.99-1-1.73a2 2 0 0 1 2-2"
          ></path>
          <path d="M7.5 13a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 0 3 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0-3"></path>
          <path d="M16.5 13a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 0 3 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0-3"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>Nuevo</span>
      </div>
      <h2>Asistente IA Contextual</h2>
      <p class="ai-description">
        ¿Tienes dudas específicas sobre una planta? Nuestra inteligencia
        artificial está entrenada con toda la información de nuestra base de
        datos para responder tus preguntas de forma detallada y precisa.
      </p>

      <div class="ai-features">
        <div class="ai-feature">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"></path>
            <path d="M12 17h.01"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Responde dudas específicas</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-feature">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <path
              d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Conversaciones naturales</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ai-feature">
          <svg
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <path d="M12 2v4"></path>
            <path d="M12 18v4"></path>
            <path d="M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83"></path>
            <path d="M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83"></path>
            <path d="M2 12h4"></path>
            <path d="M18 12h4"></path>
            <path d="M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83"></path>
            <path d="M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>Disponible 24 horas</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-preview">
        <div class="chat-bubble user">
          <span>¿Cómo cuido mi potus en invierno?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-bubble bot">
          <div class="bot-avatar">
            <svg
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path d="M12 22c4-4 8-7.5 8-12a8 8 0 1 0-16 0c0 4.5 4 8 8 12z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="bot-message">
            <p>
              En invierno, reduce el riego a cada 10-14 días y asegúrate de que
              reciba luz indirecta. El potus es resistente pero evita corrientes
              de aire frío y temperaturas menores a 15°C.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai-section {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .ai-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(46, 160, 67, 0.15);
    color: var(--accent-green-light);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ai-badge svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .ai-description {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .ai-features {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .ai-feature svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
  }

  .ai-preview {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .chat-bubble.user {
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 16px 16px 4px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    max-width: 80%;
  }

  .chat-bubble.bot {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .bot-avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: var(--bg-hover);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .bot-avatar svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }

  .bot-message {
    background: var(--bg-hover);
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 4px 16px 16px 16px;
  }

  .bot-message p {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>
